<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><title>XuetangX: Online Courses from Top Universities</title><link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://www.xuetangx.com/global"><link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://www.xuetangx.com/"><meta charset="utf-8"><meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,user-scalable=no"><meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,email=no,address=no"><meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge,chrome=1"><meta name="renderer" content="webkit"><meta name="google" content="notranslate"><meta name="msapplication-tap-highlight" content="no"><meta http-equiv="x-dns-prefetch-control" content="on"><meta http-equiv="Pragma" content="no-cache"><meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-transform "><meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-siteapp"><meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-cache"><meta http-equiv="Expires" content="0"><meta itemprop="keywords" name="keywords" content="XuetangX Online-National Excellent Online Course Learning Platform, Online Learning, Online Education, Live Online, Online Courses, Online Open Courses, Open Video Courses, Open University Courses, Computer, Artificial Intelligence, Data Science, English, Business, Economics, Training Camp, Tsinghua certification, economics, equivalent education, micro-degree, prestigious school courses, Tsinghua University, China MOOC, the first batch of national quality online open courses, courses"><meta itemprop="description" name="description" content="XuetangX is a MOOC platform launched by Tsinghua University in October 2013. It is a research exchange and achievement application platform of the Online Education Research Center of the Ministry of Education. It is the country&#x27;s first batch of double-creation demonstration base projects in 2016. The deputy secretary-general unit of the Educational Integration Research Branch is also an online education platform for the UNESCO International Engineering Education Center (ICEE). At present, the school runs more than 2,300 quality courses from Tsinghua University, Peking University, Fudan University, University of Science and Technology of China, as well as first-class universities at home and abroad, including MIT, Stanford University, University of California, Berkeley, covering 13 university subjects ."><meta itemprop="author" name="author" content="XuetangX"><meta itemprop="name" name="title" content="XuetangX: Online Courses from Top Universities"><meta property="og:title" content="XuetangX: Online Courses from Top Universities"><meta property="og:description" content="XuetangX is a MOOC platform launched by Tsinghua University in October 2013. It is a research exchange and achievement application platform of the Online Education Research Center of the Ministry of Education. It is the country&#x27;s first batch of double-creation demonstration base projects in 2016. The deputy secretary-general unit of the Educational Integration Research Branch is also an online education platform for the UNESCO International Engineering Education Center (ICEE). At present, the school runs more than 2,300 quality courses from Tsinghua University, Peking University, Fudan University, University of Science and Technology of China, as well as first-class universities at home and abroad, including MIT, Stanford University, University of California, Berkeley, covering 13 university subjects ."><meta property="og:site_name" content="XuetangX"><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="//static-cdn.xuetangx.com"><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="//qn-c27.xuetangx.com"><link ref="dns-prefetch" href="//s.xuetangx.com"><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="//storagecdn.xuetangx.com"><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="//cdn.mathjax.org"><link rel="search" type="application/opensearchdescription+xml" href="/en-opensearch.xml?v&#x3D;1.0" title="XuetangX"><link rel="shortcut icon" href="https